<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/pending-approval.png"
              alt="Pending Approval"
              class="img-fluid mb-3"
              style="max-width: 200px"
            />
            <h2 class="card-title text-primary">Application Under Review</h2>
            <div class="progress mb-3" style="height: 10px">
              <div
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-primary"
                role="progressbar"
                style="width: 50%"
                aria-valuenow="50"
                aria-valuemin="0"
                aria-valuemax="100"
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="alert alert-info">
            <p class="mb-0">
              Your mechanic application has been submitted successfully and is
              currently under review by our admin team.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card mb-4 border-0 bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title text-secondary">What happens next?</h5>
              <ol class="timeline">
                <li class="timeline-item">
                  <div class="timeline-marker bg-success"></div>
                  <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Application Submitted</h6>
                    <small class="text-muted">Completed</small>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="timeline-item">
                  <div class="timeline-marker bg-warning"></div>
                  <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Admin Review</h6>
                    <small class="text-muted">In Progress</small>
                    <p class="mt-2">
                      Our team is reviewing your credentials and documentation.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="timeline-item">
                  <div class="timeline-marker bg-secondary"></div>
                  <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Approval Decision</h6>
                    <small class="text-muted">Pending</small>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="timeline-item">
                  <div class="timeline-marker bg-secondary"></div>
                  <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Start Working</h6>
                    <small class="text-muted">Pending</small>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card mb-4 border-0 bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title text-secondary">Approval Process</h5>
              <p>
                The approval process typically takes 1-2 business days. We'll
                notify you via email once your application has been reviewed.
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                <span>We verify your identity and credentials</span>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                <span>We review your specializations and experience</span>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                <span>We check your uploaded documentation</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <p>Have questions about your application?</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
              <a
                href="mailto:support@fixonthego.com"
                class="btn btn-outline-primary"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Support
              </a>
              <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Return to Homepage
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mt-4 shadow-sm border-0">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <h5 class="card-title text-primary">Frequently Asked Questions</h5>
          <div class="accordion mt-3" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapseOne"
                >
                  How long does the approval process take?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapseOne"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  The approval process typically takes 1-2 business days. During
                  peak periods, it may take up to 3 business days.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapseTwo"
                >
                  Can I edit my application while it's pending?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapseTwo"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  No, you cannot edit your application once it's submitted. If
                  you need to make changes, please contact our support team.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item border-0">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapseThree"
                >
                  What if my application is rejected?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapseThree"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  If your application is rejected, you'll receive an email
                  explaining the reasons. You can address the issues and reapply
                  after 30 days.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Add custom CSS for timeline -->
<style>
  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline:before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: #ddd;
    left: 9px;
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
    background-color: rgba(var(--bs-primary-rgb), 0.1);
    color: var(--bs-primary);
  }

  .accordion-button:focus {
    box-shadow: none;
    border-color: rgba(var(--bs-primary-rgb), 0.25);
  }
</style>
